'''Yanille watchmen''' are [[monster]]s which can be found guarding [[Yanille]] on the 2nd floor of [[Watchtower (building)|Watchtower]] towards the western side of Yanille. They require level 65 [[Thieving]] to pickpocket and give the player 137.5 [[Thieving]] [[experience]].
== Appearance ==
The Yanillian watchmen are light skin toned men. Their uniform is an iron or steel [[helmet]], a black shirt, an iron or steel[[Chain Mail Body| chain mail body and]] black pants.

